the WordPress wonderful community, had the chance to test our plugin on a store with a huge number of products, and experienced slowdowns [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Ausilia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5577:\"<p>Today we&#8217;ve released YITH WooCommerce Wishlist 2.2.12 that, among other minor changes, addresses an important performance issue that was recently pointed out to us.</p>\n<p>Dave Hilditch from WP Intense, a member of the WordPress wonderful community, had the chance to test our plugin on a store with a huge number of products, and experienced slowdowns on the wishlist page, when visiting it as a guest user. He debugged the issue, and highlighted a section of the code that needed revision (you can read his original post about the problem <a href=\"https://www.wpintense.com/2019/07/17/performance-review-of-the-yith-wishlist-its-bad/\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>).</p>\n<p>Then, he contacted us though our official contact form, and we immediately started the revision process, to make sure that the issue could be fixed as soon as possible and provide our users with the best possible experience.</p>\n<p>After less than 24 hours from that, we&#8217;re happy to announce that the problem is solved, and a new version of the plugin is out for our users.</p>\n<p>Huge thanks go to Dave for spending his knowledge and experience to help the entire community out there, and for giving us the chance to improve our plugin.</p>\n<h2>An upcoming major release is on its way</h2>\n<p>On the same subject, we think that this is a good moment to look forward, and we&#8217;re very proud to announce that the upcoming new version 3.0 is on its way to be released.</p>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Wishlist has been out for 6 years (!) now with 700,000+ active installations, and we wanted to shake things up with this project.</p>\n<p>For this reason, the next major release will feature a big code refactoring that will assure our users that their wishlist plugin is up to date and makes use of cutting-edge technologies, complying at the same time with all WooCommerce standards and guidelines.</p>\n<p>Just for the purpose of arousing your curiosity, here is a short list of the features that we will include in version 3.0:</p>\n<p>&#8211; Unified experience for guests and logged in users<br />\n&#8211; Add variations to the wishlist<br />\n&#8211; Add-to-wishlist feature from Shop page<br />\n&#8211; New options for Add-to-Wishlist button<br />\n&#8211; New widgets for displaying wishlists</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063697\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063697\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-1.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1063697\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-1.jpg\" alt=\"Support to variations\" width=\"710\" height=\"457\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-1.jpg 710w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-1-300x193.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-1-261x168.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-1-311x200.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-1-363x234.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-1-270x174.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063697\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Now you can add a specific variation to your wishlist!</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063698\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063698\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-1.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1063698\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-1.jpg\" alt=\"Wishlist widget\" width=\"710\" height=\"729\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-1.jpg 710w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-1-292x300.jpg 292w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-1-261x268.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-1-311x319.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-1-363x373.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-1-270x277.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063698\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">New wishlist widget</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063707\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063707\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-2.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1063707\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-2.jpg\" alt=\"Add to Wishlish feature on Shop page\" width=\"710\" height=\"523\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-2.jpg 710w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-2-300x221.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-2-261x192.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-2-311x229.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-2-363x267.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-2-270x199.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063707\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Let your users add a produc to the Wishlist right from the Shop page</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We&#8217;ll soon publish our first beta version; in the meantime, we&#8217;d love to hear your opinion and suggestions.</p>\n<p>Always looking forward to offering you the best wishlist experience out there, for free! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f609.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/yit-news/heads-up-a-new-n-tasty-version-of-yith-wishlist-is-out/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"WordCamp Europe 2019 – Berlin in our hearts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-europe-2019-berlin-in-our-hearts/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-europe-2019-berlin-in-our-hearts/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 09:00:19 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1061590\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:340:\"2017 Paris 2018 Belgrade 2019 Berlin&#8230; Yes, Berlin, one the biggest cities in Europe, one of the top tourist destinations, where every corner can tell a story of the past and of the present, where culture, history, arts and technology coexist, and a city that is constantly reinventing itself for the better! The biggest WCEU [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Ausilia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11451:\"<p>2017 <strong>Paris</strong></p>\n<p>2018 <strong>Belgrade</strong></p>\n<p>2019 <strong>Berlin</strong>&#8230;</p>\n<p>Yes, Berlin, one the biggest cities in Europe, one of the top tourist destinations, where every corner can tell a story of the past and of the present, where culture, history, arts and technology coexist, and a city that is constantly reinventing itself for the better!</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063064\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063064\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1063064 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-e1563298908318.jpg\" alt=\"WCEU 2019 Berlin - Wonderful Berlin\" width=\"1000\" height=\"507\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-e1563298908318.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-e1563298908318-300x152.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-e1563298908318-768x389.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-e1563298908318-261x132.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-e1563298908318-311x158.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-e1563298908318-363x184.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-e1563298908318-270x137.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063064\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Wonderful Berlin</figcaption></figure>\n<h2>The biggest WCEU ever</h2>\n<p>This was the wonderful location that hosted WordCamp Europe 2019, with <strong>2734 actual participants (3260 sold tickets)</strong> and an awesome team that put on this event.</p>\n<p>The venue, the Estrel Hotel, was big enough to welcome the biggest number of attendees ever in a WordCamp, and still not too big to get lost. <strong>Simply perfect</strong>. This made it easy for attendees to enjoy the event and move between tracks, from a speech to the other, and visit the sponsors area and the lunch area.</p>\n<p>The contributor day was organised in two rooms, with a smart way to spot the right table: WordPress lovers crowded around the tables to contribute to every team of WordPress or simply to do some profitable networking.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063066\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063066\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1063066 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03.jpg\" alt=\"WCEU 2019 Berlin - Contributor day\" width=\"1000\" height=\"498\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-300x149.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-768x382.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-261x130.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-311x155.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-363x181.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-270x134.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063066\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opening remarks and some shots from the contributor day</figcaption></figure>\n<p>As sponsors, we were all placed in one big room right in front of the main track, which made it easy for the attendees to follow the speeches and talk with the sponsors during the breaks.</p>\n<p>Actually, it was a common feeling that people were spending time in the sponsors’ area all the time, which means they were interested in chatting with the sponsors and informing about what they can offer through WordPress. Despite that, people crowded the two tracks all the time&#8230; how can it be? Did they do the magic?</p>\n<p>Well, with more than 2700 participants (the highest number for a WordCamp ever), it’s pretty understandable that people move around and enjoy the event in all its parts.</p>\n<p>And among all this, we were also so happy to see that the new T-shirt made by YITH was appreciated as well! Grabbing a YITH T-shirt has become a WordCamp must-have for many attendees. #declarevariablesnotwar</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063067\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063067\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1063067\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04.jpg\" alt=\"WCEU 2019 Berlin - T-shirts madness\" width=\"1000\" height=\"798\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-300x239.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-768x613.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-261x208.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-311x248.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-363x290.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-270x215.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063067\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T-shirts madness</figcaption></figure>\n<p>Also, we were given the best assistance as always. <strong>We will never be thankful enough to all the great work that organizers and volunteers do every year</strong>.</p>\n<h2>Surprise surprise!</h2>\n<p>If the contributor and conference days were three full days, the after party was the cherry on top. We were delighted by an amazing concert in the hotel venue and being at the after party was so exciting.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063069\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063069\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1063069\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06.jpg\" alt=\"WCEU 2019 Berlin - After party\" width=\"1000\" height=\"514\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-300x154.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-768x395.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-261x134.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-311x160.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-363x187.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/06-270x139.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063069\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The after party</figcaption></figure>\n<p>And… even though we were not able to meet him during the conference day, we could steal him a smile and some minutes to chat.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063070\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063070\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/07.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1063070\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/07.jpg\" alt=\"WCEU 2019 Berlin - Matt Mullenweg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"514\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/07.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/07-300x154.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/07-768x395.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/07-261x134.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/07-311x160.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/07-363x187.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/07-270x139.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063070\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">We and&#8230; Matt</figcaption></figure>\n<p>Meeting the founder of WordPress always gets a thrill but it’s so amazing to see how friendly talking to him can be!</p>\n<p>So, this was a great event for us, happy and satisfied. The best part of an international event like WordCamp Europe is that you can meet people from all over the world and you always feel at home (or at least, this is my personal opinion). This is the atmosphere that one smells at WordCamps all over the world and particularly during the biggest event in Europe.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063059\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063059\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1063059\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08.jpg\" alt=\"WCEU 2019 Berlin - Thanks to everyone!\" width=\"1000\" height=\"894\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08-300x268.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08-768x687.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08-261x233.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08-311x278.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08-363x325.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/08-270x241.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063059\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thanks to everyone!</figcaption></figure>\n<h2>WordCamp Europe 2020?</h2>\n<p>And so, what about 2020? We can’t wait for the next event to come and are very curious to discover what it can offer. But how much will change in one year? Then, we’ll see&#8230;</p>\n<p>Now all we know is the location of WCEU 2020, so, looking forward to seeing what it will bring! See you all in Porto!</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1063060\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1063060\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/09.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1063060 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/09.jpg\" alt=\"WCEU 2019 Berlin - See you in Porto\" width=\"1000\" height=\"294\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/09.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/09-300x88.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/09-768x226.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/09-261x77.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/09-311x91.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/09-363x107.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/09-270x79.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1063060\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">See you in Porto</figcaption></figure>\n<h2>But before Porto&#8230;</h2>\n<p>We can meet at the following events:</p>\n<p><strong>16-18 August</strong>: <strong><a href=\"https://2019.brighton.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Brighton</a> </strong>and</p>\n<p><strong>20-21 September</strong> you will find us in 3 WordCamps at the same time: WordCamp <a href=\"https://2019.catania.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Catania</strong></a>, <strong><a href=\"https://2019.nijmegen.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" rel=\"noopener\">Nijmegen</a> </strong>and <a href=\"https://2018.pontevedra.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Pontevedra</strong></a>. See you soon!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordcamp-europe-2019-berlin-in-our-hearts/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"Web Marketing Festival 2019 – That’s how it went\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/web-marketing-festival-2019/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/web-marketing-festival-2019/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 02 Jul 2019 10:06:05 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1059082\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:326:\"How does it feel after a 3-day event that registered about 25 thousand attendees? We tell you: obviously tired. And also satisfied. Euphoric. We come back home with our luggage filled with T-shirts and expectations on our way there that is now full of ideas, energy, and new synergies. This is what the Web Marketing [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Marco Salvo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9636:\"<p>How does it feel after a 3-day event that registered about 25 thousand attendees? We tell you: obviously tired.</p>\n<p>And also satisfied.</p>\n<p>Euphoric.</p>\n<p>We come back home with our luggage filled with T-shirts and expectations on our way there that is now full of ideas, energy, and new synergies.</p>\n<p>This is what the Web Marketing Festival, the biggest Italian event/fair specialized in online marketing, gave us this year, for the third year in a row.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>21.000 attendees, 70 events, 55 training rooms, 500 exhibitors and partners, 600 startups, 500 speakers. YITH couldn&#8217;t miss it and we were there indeed, represented by <strong>Marco Salvo</strong>, <strong>Alessio Torrisi</strong>, and <strong>Andrea Grillo</strong>.</p>\n<p>Here is how the <a href=\"https://yithemes.com\"><strong>YITH</strong></a> team experienced this edition of the <strong>Web Marketing Festival</strong> starting from the location.</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-1059093 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-festival.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-festival.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-festival-300x169.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-festival-768x432.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-festival-261x147.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-festival-311x175.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-festival-363x204.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-festival-270x152.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<h2>Location of Web Marketing Festival</h2>\n<p>The event took place in the Palacongressi in Rimini, the biggest congressional building in Italy, recognized as one of the most majestic in Europe.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a huge place stretching for over 38 000 square meters where there is a plenary room with a stage where bands, artists, and celebrities from the show business performed.</p>\n<p>During the Web Marketing Festival, this amazing location came alive thanks to the several exhibitors&#8217; stands and to a group of street artists and jugglers who cheered everyone up with their joyfulness and lightheartedness.</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-1059095 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/webmarketingfestival.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/webmarketingfestival.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/webmarketingfestival-300x150.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/webmarketingfestival-768x384.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/webmarketingfestival-261x131.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/webmarketingfestival-311x156.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/webmarketingfestival-363x182.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/webmarketingfestival-270x135.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<h2>Our 3 days at Web Marketing Festival</h2>\n<p>During these 3 days, we shook hundreds of hands, hugged many friends and met a lot of new people. Our stand was a meeting point where many people, after breaking the ice, shared their projects, ideas, dreams, and ambitions with us.</p>\n<p>T-shirts we bring to the events just became a must. Many people wore the last two years&#8217; ones and approached our stand looking for the new ones. We have also met some collectors who have been knowing us for years and have all of our T-shirts!</p>\n<p>Everyone was excited about our new T-shirts “Keep calm and try turning it on and off again”. Indeed, we gave out over 700. We thought we brought so many but they kept on asking them even after the event was over and when we only had empty boxes left.</p>\n<p>The most amazing thing about this event was the cooperation among people who had a stand. We had the tangible and pleasant feeling to know each other since ever, to be everyone&#8217;s friends.</p>\n<p>We want to thank all the people who came especially to look for us at our stand and bring us their gadgets as we rarely went away (only to get some beer at the stand where they placed the beer tap). We really appreciated your help. <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-1059108 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-fetival-rimini-2019.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-fetival-rimini-2019.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-fetival-rimini-2019-300x169.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-fetival-rimini-2019-768x432.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-fetival-rimini-2019-261x147.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-fetival-rimini-2019-311x175.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-fetival-rimini-2019-363x204.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/web-marketing-fetival-rimini-2019-270x152.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<h2>And after the WMF&#8230;around Rimini in the evening</h2>\n<p>Every time we go to Rimini, we stay at the same hotel (the Baltic hotel) where we feel like at home and get spoiled by the owners Corrado and Lorella.</p>\n<p>Corrado is a funny guy who likes providing good company. Every time we came back to the hotel, exhausted by a day spent at the event, he welcomed us with one or more &#8220;spritz&#8221; or a good home-made sangria.</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-1059326 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-team-web-marketing-festival.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-team-web-marketing-festival.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-team-web-marketing-festival-300x150.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-team-web-marketing-festival-768x384.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-team-web-marketing-festival-261x131.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-team-web-marketing-festival-311x156.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-team-web-marketing-festival-363x182.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-team-web-marketing-festival-270x135.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<p>After a restoring shower, we went strolling around Rimini to enjoy its people’s politeness and to eat at Bounty, a place we hang out at since three years now that never disappoints us for its quality, quantity, and kindness.</p>\n<p>At the Bounty, in addition to Jack Sparrow in person (as you can see in the picture), we have also met other people we knew at the event.</p>\n<p>This allowed us to know some of our customers better and feel even more at home.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1059327 size-full\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-con-jeck.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-con-jeck.jpg 1000w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-con-jeck-300x150.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-con-jeck-768x384.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-con-jeck-261x131.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-con-jeck-311x156.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-con-jeck-363x182.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-con-jeck-270x135.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<h2>Ending</h2>\n<p>We feel like recommending this event to all the people involved in online marketing and, in general, to everyone working on the web. One of a kind occasion to get off from the screen, hug friends, meet new people and start, why not, new cooperations.</p>\n<p><strong>YITH</strong> thanks the organizers and all the people who made this wonderful event possible. An event that makes the difference in Italy.</p>\n<p>We will meet you again next year with our new T-shirts! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1059328 size-large\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-relax-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-relax-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-relax-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-relax-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-relax-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-relax-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-relax-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-relax-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yith-relax.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/web-marketing-festival-2019/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"It’s the community that made WordCamp Bristol truly amazing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:92:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/its-the-community-that-made-wordcamp-bristol-truly-amazing/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:100:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/its-the-community-that-made-wordcamp-bristol-truly-amazing/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 03 Jun 2019 14:13:17 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1046965\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:385:\"On 17-19 May 2019, WordCamp Bristol took place at the University of Chemistry. A well-attended event that represented the South West of England&#8217;s WordPressers as well as the many UK and international users, coders, developers, sponsors, and contributors. About Bristol WordCamp 2019 After two years, we finally got to enjoy another brilliantly organised WordCamp. Okay, [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Ronald\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19291:\"<p>On 17-19 May 2019, WordCamp Bristol took place at the University of Chemistry. A well-attended event that represented the South West of England&#8217;s WordPressers as well as the many UK and international users, coders, developers, sponsors, and contributors.</p>\n<h2>About Bristol WordCamp 2019</h2>\n<p>After two years, we finally got to enjoy another brilliantly organised WordCamp. Okay, I might be a little bit biased here as I was one of the 9 organisers and coordinated the volunteers. But as always it takes a whole group of dedicated volunteers to put up a show. This time the number of attendees had grown to almost double, which meant a new location to accommodate this fantastic community. This is not an exaggeration as the vibe, inclusion, and accessibility meant that everyone felt welcome. There was also a big emphasis on creating a low carbon footprint and &#8216;being green&#8217;. I think few people would disagree that being conscious of these factors is a bad thing.</p>\n<h3>Day 1- the contributor day</h3>\n<p>The contributor day took place right by the water called The Pavilion, No1 Hannover Quay. Various contributions were made to WordPress from theme reviews to support and WordPress TV. However, I wonder how you could stay focused in such a lovely location and view. In the evening this was transformed to the social venue and to thank all the sponsors, volunteers, speakers and organisers.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047745\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047745\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047745 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs12.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047745\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Contributor day</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047738\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047738\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047738 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs05.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047738\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Volunteers ready to welcome attendees</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047741\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047741\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047741 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs08.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047741\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The YITH stand &#8211; ready to hand out swag</figcaption></figure>\n<h3>Day 2 &#8211; Conference day and after party</h3>\n<p>An early start for as I needed to set up the sponsorship table before the attendees would embark onto the University of Bristol&#8217;s Chemistry department. The location and venue was a big part of the success of this year&#8217;s WordCamp. Two lecture rooms, a quiet room and a huge space for all attendees to mingle with sponsors while drinking coffee or having lunch. It is usually the case that the first part of the day just flies by. Many WordPressers love a bit of swag and our #KeepCalmAndClearCache t-shirts did not disappoint the Bristol crowd. What was lovely to hear was that so many of those who came to see me are users of our plugins. This is one of the main reasons why we attend so many WordPress events, to meet you&#8230; It is also a great opportunity to hear feedback, discuss new launches and get ideas by talking to users.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047748\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047748\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047748 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs01.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047748\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lots of interest from the attendees</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047744\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047744\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047744 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs11.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047744\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Vegetarian lunchtime buffet</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047737\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047737\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047737 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"people socializing\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs04.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047737\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Evening social at the Watershed</figcaption></figure>\n<p>The evening social took place at the Watershed. You get the chance to catch up with old and new friends whilst reflecting on all the new things you&#8217;ve learned that day. &#8216;Make your own burritos&#8217; is a great way to feed a large group with various dietary requirements. The atmosphere was a bit too good to not finish the evening in various other bars down by the quay.</p>\n<h3>Day 3 &#8211; Conference day</h3>\n<p>Another fine and quiet morning marching up the hill for a slightly later start than the day before&#8230; For those that attended WordCamp Bristol, you probably regretted not getting a hotel higher up the hill as it was most certainly a steep one. As usual, the catering was set up and coffee and biscuits were welcoming the WordPressers that would attend day two. A whole day of 2 tracks with speakers lined up kept everyone wondering which talk to attend till the last moment. Often to make mental notes to catch up on the &#8216;other&#8217; talk on WordPress TV. As most YITH plugin users probably met up with Ronald on Saturday, it was more obvious that on Sunday it was the turn of WordPressers that wanted to find out more. This is just as important to us, as WordCamps are a great way to introduce new users to the extended world of WooCommerce.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047735\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047735\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047735 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"keepcalmandclearcache t-shirt\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs02.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047735\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Happy attendee <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047740\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047740\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047740 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"holding t-shirts\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs07.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047740\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">More happy attendees <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047742\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047742\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047742 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs09.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047742\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Who wouldn&#8217;t be happy with cool swag <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f609.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></figcaption></figure>\n<h2>YITH as a gold sponsor of WordCamp Bristol</h2>\n<p>As a company, we felt honoured to be part of WordCamp Bristol and to be able to sponsor such a great and well-run event.</p>\n<p><strong>Thank you to each and every one of you</strong></p>\n<p>As much as I&#8217;d like to thank every person that made WordCamp Bristol possible, it would be an impossible task. Hannah and Janice, who were the leads, most certainly know how to put a super team together. They, in turn, the volunteers, speakers, venue, staff and every ticket holder they invited to join in one of the best WordCamp experiences of this year. It got me and the rest of YITH inspired and already looking forward to the next one.</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047743\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047743\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047743 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"conference projector\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs10.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047743\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">WordCamp leads doing their Thank You&#8217;s</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047746\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047746\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047746 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"group of volunteers\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs13.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047746\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thanks to all the volunteers and organisers</figcaption></figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047747\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047747\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047747 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"applause\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs14.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047747\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Attendees certainly showed their appreciation</figcaption></figure>\n<h3>WordPress Community and what it means for YITH</h3>\n<p>All of our staff contribute to the community in one way or another, whether it is by translating, coding or giving up time to teach the next generation about WordPress. While WordCamp Bristol was in full swing, two of our developers were at WordCamp Bari contributing, speaking and also sponsoring. You see, we love WordPress here at YITH!</p>\n<h3>Upcoming WordCamp events to meet us</h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1047739\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1047739\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img class=\"wp-image-1047739 size-medium\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Ronald Gijsel\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-300x225.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-768x576.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-261x196.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-311x233.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-363x272.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06-270x203.jpg 270w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wcbrs06.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1047739\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Join Ronald from YITH at the next event</figcaption></figure>\n<p>The next WordCamp is most certainly going to be the biggest and the best. Yes, you guessed it&#8230; on 21 and 22 June, aver 3000 WordPress enthusiasts will embark on Berlin to listen, socialize, engage and get entertained by the WordPress Community. Many of the Bristol team will be there too and we will most certainly keep an eye out for them. Will you come to Berlin? Make sure you let us know on social media or during the event.</p>\n<p>Further on in the year, we will be in <a href=\"https://2019.brighton.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Brighton</a> (UK) <a href=\"https://2019.catania.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Catania</a> (It) and <a href=\"https://2019.nijmegen.wordcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nijmegen</a> (NL) with further WordCamps in the planning. If you&#8217;d like us to get involved in your WordPress community event, why not <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/contact/\">contact us</a> and we would consider supporting it.</p>\n<p>Looking forward to seeing you at the next community event!</p>\n<p>And finally, there is only one thing to remember&#8230;</p>\n<h4>#KeepCalmAndClearCache</h4>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>(photo credits: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Aleks_Creative\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Aleks</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/La_Lole\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lorena</a>)</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:97:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/its-the-community-that-made-wordcamp-bristol-truly-amazing/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:122:\"WordPress lovers gathering again in Turin, this time under the viral slogan #keepcalmandclearcache – WordCamp Turin 2019\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:150:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordpress-lovers-gathering-again-in-turin-this-time-under-the-viral-slogan-keepcalmandclearcache-wordcamp-turin-2019/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:158:\"https://yithemes.com/blog/events/wordpress-lovers-gathering-again-in-turin-this-time-under-the-viral-slogan-keepcalmandclearcache-wordcamp-turin-2019/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 29 Apr 2019 14:13:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://yithemes.com/?p=1035893\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:344:\"It’s an annual tradition now for us at YITH, we couldn’t miss the awesome event organized by the WordPress community in Turin: WordCamp Turin 2019! Hosted in the location of Toolbox Coworking, it started on April 5th with the Contributor Day. In the big room named “Keynote”, the attendees were crowding around the tables with [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"YITH Support Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6171:\"<p dir=\"ltr\">It’s an annual tradition now for us at YITH, we couldn’t miss the <strong>awesome event organized by the WordPress community in Turin</strong>: WordCamp Turin 2019!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Hosted in the location of Toolbox Coworking, it started on April 5th with the Contributor Day.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the big room named “Keynote”, the attendees were crowding around the tables with one common goal, contributing to WordPress for one whole day, be they developers, graphic designers, polyglots, marketers or mere WordPress lovers.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As soon as we arrived, after taking a cup of coffee, we sat down at <strong>WP Core table and worked on contributing to WordPress</strong> as well.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The location was perfect for the Contributor Day (as it was in the past years too) and everything was organised with great attention to the detail.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Saturday 6th April was the high point of the event: the conference day!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The first speeches began at 9:30 with topics ranging from development, content management, SEO, marketing, business and much more.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1037085\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2126\" height=\"785\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4.jpg 2126w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-300x111.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-768x284.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-1024x378.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-261x96.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-311x115.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-363x134.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-4-270x100.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2126px) 100vw, 2126px\" /></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Right from the start of the event and during the breaks, our t-shirts literally flew off the shelves!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The slogan printed on them <strong>“Keep calm and clear cache”</strong> won all people approaching the booth, they couldn’t help asking for one! Some of them use to collect all our t-shirts and could not absolutely miss this new piece.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1037086\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1672\" height=\"785\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2.jpg 1672w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-300x141.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-768x361.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-1024x481.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-261x123.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-311x146.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-363x170.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-2-270x127.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1672px) 100vw, 1672px\" /></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Among the many people that stopped to talk, to our great satisfaction, we could notice that most of them are using our products. As developers, it made us proud to hear statements like “I’ve been using your plugins for a while now, and I couldn’t do without them”.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1037087\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1672\" height=\"785\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1.jpg 1672w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-300x141.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-768x361.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-1024x481.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-261x123.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-311x146.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-363x170.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-1-270x127.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1672px) 100vw, 1672px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1037088\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2012\" height=\"735\" srcset=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3.jpg 2012w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-300x110.jpg 300w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-768x281.jpg 768w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-1024x374.jpg 1024w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-261x95.jpg 261w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-311x114.jpg 311w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-363x133.jpg 363w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Senza-titolo-3-270x99.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2012px) 100vw, 2012px\" /></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">We also had the opportunity and pleasure to meet familiar faces and old friends. Not only could we hold business conversations with all of them, but also we spent a wonderful evening at the after party, held in the same location: board games, ping-pong, table football, karaoke… well, we did not miss anything!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>We want to thank both all the organisers and volunteers</strong> that worked hard to make the WordCamp result in such a successful and enjoyable event, and all the attendees who took part in the event: it couldn’t have been so great without them!</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}